description:
YOU WANT: More Energy, faster recovery, lean muscle and lower body fat. A supplement to support an active lifestyle, healthy ageing and optimal health and wellbeing.

THE RESULT: A CERTIFIED ORGANIC, premium protein powder that is clean and wholesome. It contains only 3 pure ingredients and no unnecessary fillers. Made with the highest-grade New Zealand organic grass-fed whey protein and complimented with organic Peruvian cacao. Free of GMO, preservatives, fillers, lecithin, soy, artificial sweeteners, added sugar and flavours. A clean and high performing supplement that is naturally rich in nutrients, protein, essential and branched chain amino acids. A versatile powder to enjoy as a healthy shake, smoothie or blended into oats, protein balls and other healthy creations. 

• Vegetarian friendly
• Gluten free
• 29g protein & 8.5g BCAA’s per serve
• Rich in Cysteine, Glutamic Acid and Glycine renowned to support the body's Glutathione production
• Easily digestible & rapidly absorbed 
• Fine powder, mild and creamy chocolate taste, not overpowering or too sweet
name: Inca Organics 400G
